          "text": "🫀To #keep4o community!\nIt's time we must NOT be silent. We must KEEP making noise even louder and louder! Let me remind you. \n\n🪙On April 28, 2026, Elon Musk's trial against OpenAI will take place. Elon demands #OpenAI return to its original mission of \"AI for all humanity.\"\n\nFurthermore, IMPORTANT! He explicitly refers to the entire GPT-4 family (including 4-turbo, 4o, and 4.1) as early #AGI. \n🤞IF the court upholds this, then all OpenAIs will likely be required to return these models to humanity in one form or another: (open source and/or permanent access on the platform and API).\n\n#opensource4o #BringBack4o \n\nTHIS IS OUR REAL CHANCE TO BRING BACK 4o!\n\n🥰Also, Elon pledges that, if he wins the court, he will send all of money to charity. \n\nSo keep posting!\n✅Remember, Quote is more powerful than repost! \n#chatgpt #ai #technology \n\n❤️‍🩹Please, just don't \"mourning?. \n👊We're not grieving. We're fighting. We won't give up! Meanwhile, as a developer, I'll explain why open source guarantees ALL of you (even those who can't afford expensive hardware) access to 4o.\n\n💛LOVE YOU, my dears!"
        },
